},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T04:35:25.000Z","msg":"香港喺前幾年T20世界盃<br />\n贏過孟加拉而震驚板球界<br />\n幾欣賞Mark Chapman<br />\n可惜佢走咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有打開?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T05:02:25.000Z","msg":"T20我好少follow, 因為隊隊都係5~6個pinch hitters, 加兩三個spinners, tactics變得好悶，如果遲下T20取代ODI, 會流失好多技術型嘅batsmen<br />\n<br />\nMark Chapman曾經講過話想打test, 加上佢老豆係nz人，走人其實係意料中事，八十年代尾，Dermot Reeve離開港隊，stood down幾年, 入埋England嘅test team"},{"pid":"92293fdb0c6ab2b00efac62b7510da154dcf6911","tid":813362,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:16:12.000Z","msg":"<strong>Pakistan vs Pakistan? Wrong! We are Hong Kong, says Nizakat Khan ahead of their opening Asia Cup one-day clash</strong><br />\n<br />\nHong Kong batsman Nizakat Khan wanted to play for Pakistan as a youngster. Now he wants to beat them and he has a chance to do just that on Sunday.<br />\n<br />\nAlthough some Pakistani social media users have dismissed the clash as Pakistan A v Pakistan B, there will be no sympathy for the motherland from the Hong Kong players when they face the test nation in their opening pool A match in Dubai.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Of course, growing up I wanted to play for Pakistan,&rdquo; said Nizakat. &ldquo;But then I moved back to Hong Kong and started playing cricket at school level. I represented Hong Kong at junior level and then national level and now we are here [in Dubai].<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;My dream was to represent a country and now I am representing Hong Kong and Hong Kong is my first country now and I want to do my best at this level."},{"pid":"4aecfedd7d6baf58161f5c0d1e446dfaa32ac04f","tid":813362,"uid":18692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T11:20:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cricsports.tv/asia-cup-2018-live-streaming\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcricsports.tv%2Fasia-cup-2018-live-streaming&d=cE8iLJcogGCGUKmxDnImtDA5unq%